{"results":[{"aya":"148","id":3936,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"他们便归信他，我使他们享乐至一定期。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"149","id":3937,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你问他们吧！你的主有许多女儿，他们却有多少儿子呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"150","id":3938,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"还是我曾将众天神造成女性的，他们曾眼见我的创造呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"151","id":3939,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"真的，他们因为自己的悖谬，必定要说：","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"152","id":3940,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"真主已生育了。他们确是说谎者。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"153","id":3941,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"难道他不要儿子，却要女儿吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"154","id":3942,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你们有什么理由？你们怎么这样判断呢？","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-21.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-23.json"}}